## Limitations

The analysis is based on available literature and may not capture all perspectives, particularly those that highlight the positive impacts of unions. The findings are primarily drawn from sources that critique unions, which may introduce bias. Additionally, the economic impact of unions can vary significantly across different industries and regions, which this report may not fully address.

